{"tid":858107,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"龍心：正式宣佈參選九西補選","createTime":"2018-10-11T14:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T14:35:14.000Z","uid":158149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d5e86d0800644d85441e94687989e0eb0fd2e2d","tid":858107,"uid":158149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:25:35.000Z","msg":"自稱「龍心」的網絡紅人林克霖，近月再度「出山」，各種出位言論繼續引起網民熱議，日前更有傳言指他將出戰立法會九龍西補選。今日龍心帶同5萬元選舉按金踩上蘋果《你問我答》節目，正式宣佈參選。<br />\n究竟龍心為甚麼決定參選？他又是如何看另外三位已交表的候選人？隱藏在各種人格背後是一個甚麼樣的故事？今晚9點鐘，請留意《你問我答》。<br />\n<br />\n轉自蘋果日報<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/222527_e913ea604fe8974b21020e9d2906cea5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F222527_e913ea604fe8974b21020e9d2906cea5.jpg&h=855b8c89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c62bcd481c8264e6c483b52c96d4ea5d9d1ecee","tid":858107,"uid":158149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就拎五萬出黎"},{"pid":"b9140cb9adc1389bb898eb4fb05bec5c375468af","tid":858107,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"做咩咁傻"},{"pid":"1bf7a6fe4ee93fd9a376f3e017d214392ca905b1","tid":858107,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9140cb9adc1389bb898eb4fb05bec5c375468af","tid":858107,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"做咩咁傻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:31:44.000Z","msg":"有眼你睇，仲問"},{"pid":"d7700b30ddece12fe738631d4f9bebb427f3d81b","tid":858107,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bf7a6fe4ee93fd9a376f3e017d214392ca905b1","tid":858107,"uid":52417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9140cb9adc1389bb898eb4fb05bec5c375468af","tid":858107,"uid":85557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T14:30:21.000Z","msg":"做咩咁傻"},"ci